fact.io.hdureader

Class Header

  • java.lang.Object
    • fact.io.hdureader.Header

  • public class Header
extends Object
    This class represents a header in the HDU of fits file. The values in the header can be accessed via convenience 'get' methods for the main data types. HISTORY and COMMENT strings are also saved.

    Created by mackaiver on 18/11/16.

      • date

        public Optional<ZonedDateTime> date()
        According to the FITS standard a header can contain a DATE keyword. This method returns a LocalDateTime if a date can be found in the header.
        Returns:
        date stored in the HDU header
